25struct ResultMetadata::Value
26{
27 virtual ~Value() = default;
28 virtual int toInteger(int fallback) const {
29 return fallback;
30 }
31 virtual std::wstring toString() const {
32 return std::wstring();
33 }
34 virtual std::list<ByteArray> toByteArrayList() const {
35 return std::list<ByteArray>();
36 }
37 virtual std::shared_ptr<CustomData> toCustomData() const {
38 return nullptr;
39 }
40};

42struct ResultMetadata::IntegerValue : public Value
43{
44 int value;
45 explicit IntegerValue(int v) : value(v) {}
46 int toInteger(int) const override {
47 return value;
48 }
49 std::wstring toString() const override {

83{
